{"tid":2397433,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家樂真係好食過大快活？","createTime":"2021-02-06T12:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T18:17:33.000Z","uid":171786,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4b55bc6e2ed5812ce901bae9de426e7d4fa26fe9","tid":2397433,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e6rq2ka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6rq2ka.jpg&h=a3f0186f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n💎 大家樂 💎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CafedeCoralfastfood/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCafedeCoralfastfood%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=39ece4e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CafedeCoralfastfood/</a><br />\n-<br />\n😡1.派嬲 💬2.留言 🙅🏻♀3.永久抵制 👍🏻4.互Like留言<br />\n-<br />\n大家樂CEO羅開光同大快活CEO羅開揚係堂兄弟，但點解前者要抵制，後者又幫襯得？三個原因。<br />\n<br />\n第一，2015年大家樂業績倒退15%，大家樂CEO將原因歸咎於佔中，但同期大快活純利增長三成，可見大家樂賴得就賴。<br />\n<br />\n第二，雨革後，杜汶澤事業陷入低潮，大快活繼續搵杜代言，大快活CEO更加讚過杜「夠真，有活力，夠開心」，而杜亦稱對方係「一間重感情嘅餐廳」；<br />\n<br />\n第三，大快活前年10月話再無計劃喺TVB賣廣告，至今仍然信守承諾，而大家樂上年年底就贊助《後生仔傾吓偈》。當然，有黃當然食黃先，但如果無，都可以考慮吓大快活💚"},{"pid":"a8bdb235b475b65a1138fed8937ada09301c7fac","tid":2397433,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa0b99a4b50aa509c8df342119c19355406838f","tid":2397433,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a10a03b050f0cf97d59dece365b98cb7a8d2611","tid":2397433,"uid":265010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc5829c8725cdc53b5bf517637cc08ffc0a90e4","tid":2397433,"uid":315760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:19:52.000Z","msg":"可能大快活有啲嘢食真係未如人意<br />\n但至少我覺得食佢抵過大家樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501b2b08e08cbb4d9243e3d9f759864d334552cf","tid":2397433,"uid":126731,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:22:17.000Z","msg":"大家樂全部支那料，勁難食。"},{"pid":"e43d8414ad1d70e1bde2f1e6d48bcd13c42009f0","tid":2397433,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:22:58.000Z","msg":"大家食係的確好過活仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf302ebd51d9014361f90974e597feaa5415132","tid":2397433,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a445de422d2cd8b09096a66c4c71b4eafc98ee8a","tid":2397433,"uid":40425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:17:29.000Z","msg":"大快活奶茶打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ea71065dade62a25053f1fc81a9402b204152a","tid":2397433,"uid":257951,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:21:01.000Z","msg":"雖然未入嚟已經知你係標題黨 不過大快活好食過大家樂不嬲都係共識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca0ff30c54e2bd80138f02eb82acfdded9d4616","tid":2397433,"uid":324847,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"c3ea71065dade62a25053f1fc81a9402b204152a","tid":2397433,"uid":257951,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:21:01.000Z","msg":"雖然未入嚟已經知你係標題黨 不過大快活好食過大家樂不嬲都係共識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.g